&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Quadbridge is a fast-growing North American IT solutions provider,&amp;nbsp;empowering businesses to navigate complex challenges daily, through strong partnerships with leading technology providers and close collaboration with our team and customers.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;With locations in Kitchener, Montreal and Vancouver, we strive to create an energetic, fun workplace where ambitious, like-minded teammates collaborate, innovate, and thrive as we continue to grow our national footprint.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are Quadbridge. See how we’re building tomorrow’s solutions, together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Quadbridge is looking for a driven Account Manager in the Greater Vancouver Area. This is a high-impact, sales role focused on building strong local relationships, prospecting new clients, and delivering tailored IT solutions through face-to-face selling and relationship building. You&#39;ll be the face of Quadbridge in the field — meeting with decision-makers, uncovering needs, and driving value through a consultative, solution-based approach. If you&#39;re a self-starter, with a builder mindset, who thrives on relationship-driven selling, this is your opportunity to make a real impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospecting for new accounts via calls, emails, networking and strategic partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with cross functional teams of Product and Solution Experts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and facilitate in-person meetings with senior contacts within customer accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create sales opportunities by leveraging new and existing customer relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively manage sales pipeline through CRM tools on a regular basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Value-based and solution selling at all levels of the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively with partner community to create opportunities, align with strategy and obtain additional support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing learning and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 2-5 years of relevant sales experience, with a focus on managing mid-to-large size accounts and navigating complex, long sales cycles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record in selling project-based IT solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience conducting face-to-face sales calls (an asset)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An established client portfolio is a strong asset to accelerate success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial mindset with a self-driven approach to success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently positive attitude, fostering strong relationships with both clients and team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for emerging technologies, staying up to date with industry trends, and working with cutting-edge solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Microsoft products and technologies, preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Quadbridge?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Invest in Your Future&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Benefit from our RRSP program to help you plan ahead.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grow With Us&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Take advantage of ongoing professional training and development opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comprehensive Coverage&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– A complete health, dental, life and LTD insurance plan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Top-Tier Equipment&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– We provide everything you need to do your best work.&lt;/li&gt

